title: YellowBrickRoad
subTitle: An expedition sets out to explore a mysterious forest where the residents of a town all died.

title: Outlier
subTitle: A woman escapes her abusive ex-boyfriend with the help of a kind stranger, but his intentions are not yet clear.

title: Everybody Dies by the End
subTitle: A documentary crew follows cult classic horror director Alfred Costella as he makes his final film, an all-practical masterpiece with a dark twist.

title: Haunted House Of Pancakes
subTitle: Trapped inside a nightmarish diner on Halloween night, a waiter and a college student must fight back against bloodthirsty food out for revenge. Will they escape the clutches of the Haunted House of Pancakes or fall victim to the food apocalypse?

title: Incident at Guilt Ridge
subTitle: Two outlaws in the 1880s take up a lucrative assignment that lands them in the jaws of danger. Only time can tell if they will make it or get slaughtered.

title: A Prayer for the Damned
subTitle: Thirteen years after the American Civil War, three mysterious characters converge upon a strange New Mexico Territory town on a quest for a lost Confederate fortune.

title: Shed
subTitle: A group of friends party in a cabin in the woods, unaware that skin-stealing monsters are about to prey on them.

title: Time of the Witch
subTitle: A small town in Arizona. The Townspeople are terrified. They are convinced that Aliens will invade soon. The priest blames the townspeople for turning their backs on God. A young woman, Sophia, hears voices telling her she must save everyone. She heals Richard, a broken and suicidal man. When she rejects him, he accuses her of drugging and seducing him. The townspeople accuse her of witchcraft, of ruining a respectable man. They blame her for all their troubles.
